<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>His Hands | Give Water. Give Hope.</title>

  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: "Segoe UI", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      background: #ffffff;
      color: #08304b;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* HEADER */
    header {
      background: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px 8%;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e6f1f7;
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 100;
    }

    header h1 {
      font-size: 26px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #0077b6;
    }

    nav a {
      margin: 0 14px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #08304b;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .header-btn {
      background: #0077b6;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 10px 22px;
      border-radius: 30px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    /* HERO */
    .hero {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #e8f4fb, #ffffff);
      padding: 90px 8%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 60px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .hero-text {
      flex: 1;
    }

    .hero-text h2 {
      font-size: 52px;
      color: #0077b6;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .hero-text p {
      font-size: 19px;
      max-width: 520px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .hero-text a {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #0077b6;
      color: white;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      border-radius: 32px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .hero-img {
      flex: 1;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .hero-img img {
      max-width: 100%;
      border-radius: 20px;
    }

    /* SECTIONS */
    section {
      padding: 90px 8%;
    }

    .center {
      text-align: center;
    }

    h3 {
      font-size: 36px;
      color: #0077b6;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    /* MISSION */
    .mission p {
      max-width: 750px;
      margin: auto;
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    /* PROJECTS */
    .projects {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
      gap: 35px;
      margin-top: 50px;
    }

    .card {
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      overflow: hidden;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .card img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 210px;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    .card h4 {
      margin: 22px 0 10px;
      font-size: 20px;
    }

    .card a {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      color: #0077b6;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    /* DONATION */
    .donation {
      background: #0077b6;
      color: white;
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 70px 8%;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .donation h3 {
      color: white;
    }

    .donation p {
      max-width: 650px;
      margin: 20px auto 35px;
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .donation a {
      background: white;
      color: #0077b6;
      padding: 16px 36px;
      border-radius: 35px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    /* HELP */
    .help {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
      gap: 40px;
      margin-top: 50px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .help div {
      background: #f0f8fd;
      padding: 35px;
      border-radius: 20px;
    }

    /* FOOTER */
    footer {
      background: #08304b;
      color: white;
      padding: 45px 8%;
      text-align: center;
    }

    footer p {
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-top: 10px;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
  <h1>His Hands</h1>
  <nav>
    <a href="#">Home</a>
    <a href="#">About</a>
    <a href="#">Projects</a>
    <a href="#">Get Involved</a>
    <a href="#">Donate</a>
    <a href="#">Contact</a>
  </nav>
  <a href="#" class="header-btn">Give Water. Give Hope.</a>
</header>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-text">
    <h2>Every Drop Brings Life.</h2>
    <p>Join His Hands to bring clean water, dignity, and hope to communities in need.</p>
    <a href="#">Donate Now</a>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-img">
    <!-- 2D HERO ILLUSTRATION GOES HERE -->
    <img src="images/hero.png" alt="Smiling villagers gathered around a clean water well">
  </div>
</section>

<section class="mission center">
  <h3>Our Mission</h3>
  <p>
    We believe access to clean water is a fundamental human right.
    His Hands partners with communities to build sustainable water solutions
    that restore health, dignity, and opportunity.
  </p>
</section>

<section>
  <h3 class="center">Featured Projects</h3>

  <div class="projects">
    <div class="card">
      <img src="images/project1.jpg" alt="Water well project">
      <h4>Clean Water Wells</h4>
      <a href="#">See Project</a>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <img src="images/project2.jpg" alt="School support">
      <h4>Education Support</h4>
      <a href="#">See Project</a>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <img src="images/project3.jpg" alt="Community aid">
      <h4>Community Development</h4>
      <a href="#">See Project</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="donation">
  <h3>Be the Reason a Community Thrives</h3>
  <p>
    Your donation helps fund boreholes, clean water systems,
    and life-changing projects for families and children.
  </p>
  <a href="#">Donate Today</a>
</section>

<section class="center">
  <h3>How You Can Help</h3>

  <div class="help">
    <div>
      <h4>Donate</h4>
      <p>Provide clean water and save lives.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h4>Volunteer</h4>
      <p>Give your time to meaningful causes.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h4>Share</h4>
      <p>Spread hope and raise awareness.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <h4>His Hands</h4>
  <p>Â© 2026 His Hands. All rights reserved.</p>
</footer>

</body>
  </html>
